title: GO HIGH LEVEL ROCKSTAR
job_overview:
In search of: 
 • Expert in Go High Level (minimum 1 year experience, proven results required)
 • You think in flows, logic, automation, and conversion
 • Fluent in English with excellent communication and documentation skills
 • Comfortable managing large lists, tags, automations, and workflows
 • Able to take strategic direction and translate it into system execution
 • Obsessed with optimization and user experience
 • Detail-oriented, solution-focused, and self-managed
 • Bonus: You’ve worked in real estate, coaching, or digital marketing environments


WHAT WE OFFER
 • Long-term growth inside a purpose-driven, mission-minded organization
 • Hands-on collaboration with high-level leadership
 • Consistent hours, fast feedback, and room to grow into leadership
 • Opportunity to innovate and create meaningful systems that scale impact
 • Access to our full suite of projects, including: real estate operations, coaching funnels, live event automation, academy student journeys, and more


Commitment: Part-Time to Full-Time (Long-Term Growth Role)

Timezone: Must overlap with Eastern Standard Time (8 AM – 1 PM EST minimum)
